1
00:01:36,570 --> 00:01:40,030
[NORTHWARD]

2
00:01:40,140 --> 00:01:41,870
[Episode 30]

3
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,490
[Notice Board of Fenghua Express]

4
00:01:53,930 --> 00:01:54,759
Fenghua.

5
00:01:57,350 --> 00:01:58,120
Fenghua!

6
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:23,020
Hello?

7
00:02:23,040 --> 00:02:24,200
Where are you?

8
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:25,400
I brought you food.

9
00:02:25,420 --> 00:02:26,420
I'm at your doorstep.

10
00:02:27,060 --> 00:02:28,329
I'm going home for the New Year.

11
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,930
I'm on my way to the train station.

12
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:30,930
What?

13
00:02:32,490 --> 00:02:34,210
Aren't you going back with us?

14
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:36,130
I was planning to drive back.

15
00:02:36,310 --> 00:02:37,870
Driving is too tiring.

16
00:02:37,910 --> 00:02:39,190
The high-speed train is more convenient.

17
00:02:40,950 --> 00:02:42,880
This is so sudden.

18
00:02:43,370 --> 00:02:45,370
Going home without saying a word?

19
00:02:47,050 --> 00:02:48,360
I miss my mom.

20
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,870
My mom misses me too.

21
00:02:50,110 --> 00:02:52,130
I don't have much going on here anyway.

22
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:53,630
When are you going back?

23
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:54,920
By car or train?

24
00:02:58,380 --> 00:02:59,170
Hello?

25
00:03:02,830 --> 00:03:03,580
Fenghua.

26
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:07,330
What's going on with you lately?

27
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:09,430
Didn't we agree to go back together?

28
00:03:11,020 --> 00:03:13,250
The signal is bad. I'll hang up.

29
00:03:35,510 --> 00:03:37,810
Mei, preparing for the New Year?

30
00:03:38,010 --> 00:03:39,400
When do your holidays start?

31
00:03:38,060 --> 00:03:42,340
[By the Canal]

32
00:03:39,670 --> 00:03:40,240
Mom.

33
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,680
Have you prepared the New Year goods?

34
00:03:42,110 --> 00:03:42,790
Mom!

35
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,150
Fenghua?

36
00:03:47,190 --> 00:03:49,329
Fenghua! Why are you back?

37
00:03:50,790 --> 00:03:52,530
Why didn't you tell me you were coming back?

38
00:03:52,590 --> 00:03:54,800
I could've picked you up at the station.

39
00:03:54,820 --> 00:03:56,200
Didn't I tell you?

40
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,280
I don't have much to do there,

41
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,360
so I came back early

42
00:03:58,380 --> 00:03:59,579
to spend a few more days with you.

43
00:03:59,610 --> 00:04:00,710
Why have you lost weight?

44
00:04:00,990 --> 00:04:02,420
Come on, let's go home.

45
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:05,010
What about Wanghe and the others?

46
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:06,920
They'll be here in a few days, I guess.

47
00:04:06,940 --> 00:04:08,480
The food delivery industry is busy now.

48
00:04:08,590 --> 00:04:09,590
We're in parcel delivery.

49
00:04:09,590 --> 00:04:11,680
Near the end of the year, there's not much business.

50
00:04:12,620 --> 00:04:13,770
Right on time.

51
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:16,050
Look at the smoked fish Mr. Zhou gave us.

52
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:17,040
I'll cook it for you tonight.

53
00:04:17,070 --> 00:04:17,930
You're in for a treat.

54
00:04:19,829 --> 00:04:20,730
Fenghua.

55
00:04:21,829 --> 00:04:23,610
Fenghua, are you up?

56
00:04:24,070 --> 00:04:25,390
Do you know what time it is?

57
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:28,950
Fenghua, get up now.

58
00:04:28,970 --> 00:04:31,310
How can you stay inside in the day?

59
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,270
Get up, get up.

60
00:04:32,270 --> 00:04:33,200
Get some sunshine.

61
00:04:33,270 --> 00:04:34,800
It's so sunny outside today.

62
00:04:34,830 --> 00:04:35,770
Come on, my baby.

63
00:04:36,430 --> 00:04:37,360
I'm tired.

64
00:04:37,830 --> 00:04:38,600
Tired?

65
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:39,680
Too tired to get some sun?

66
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,430
Look at this princess.

67
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:43,490
Look at your messy hair.

68
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:46,409
It's like a chicken's nest.

69
00:04:47,990 --> 00:04:48,680
Wait...

70
00:04:48,710 --> 00:04:50,540
Why are you losing so much hair?

71
00:04:52,580 --> 00:04:54,860
I have too many things to worry about.

72
00:04:54,890 --> 00:04:56,820
It's already better than before.

73
00:04:56,950 --> 00:04:58,700
There was a time when I was almost bald.

74
00:04:58,830 --> 00:04:59,710
Look at my hairline.

75
00:05:03,340 --> 00:05:04,180
Look at you.

76
00:05:04,270 --> 00:05:05,270
You're exhausted.

77
00:05:05,730 --> 00:05:07,140
Tired from work.

78
00:05:07,430 --> 00:05:08,610
Quit your job and come home.

79
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,990
Don't stay in Beijing anymore.

80
00:05:10,730 --> 00:05:11,580
I'll take care of you.

81
00:05:13,330 --> 00:05:15,250
Your dad and I don't rely on your earnings.

82
00:05:15,280 --> 00:05:16,430
Just stay at home.

83
00:05:16,450 --> 00:05:18,120
There will always be hot soup and meals for you.

84
00:05:18,150 --> 00:05:20,270
I promise to raise you nice and plump.

85
00:05:22,270 --> 00:05:23,720
Say something. What do you think?

86
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:28,960
What's wrong?

87
00:05:31,630 --> 00:05:32,360
Nothing.

88
00:05:33,650 --> 00:05:35,570
I just suddenly feel like singing.

89
00:05:38,260 --> 00:05:40,180
When Siyi was here,

90
00:05:41,030 --> 00:05:42,100
I didn't dare sing.

91
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:44,400
I didn't want to upset her.

92
00:05:46,070 --> 00:05:47,780
Now I can sing freely.

93
00:05:50,270 --> 00:05:55,870
♫In this world, there's no one else like Mom♫

94
00:05:56,340 --> 00:06:02,270
♫A child with a mom is like treasure♫

95
00:06:02,830 --> 00:06:03,640
Gosh.

96
00:06:03,660 --> 00:06:05,940
Still as crazy as when you were little.

97
00:06:06,420 --> 00:06:08,780
Let's see which boy can handle you in the future.

98
00:06:11,070 --> 00:06:16,720
♫Throw yourself into Mom's embrace♫

