102
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:41,070
♫Throw yourself into Mom's embrace♫

103
00:06:41,070 --> 00:06:45,120
♫Endless happiness♫

104
00:06:55,770 --> 00:06:57,720
How's your tofu pudding shop doing?

105
00:06:57,750 --> 00:07:00,890
It's been great. I'm earning more than when I had a street stall.

106
00:07:00,910 --> 00:07:02,600
And I'm sheltered from the wind and sun.

107
00:07:02,630 --> 00:07:03,550
It's comfortable.

108
00:07:04,060 --> 00:07:06,760
If you move back and want something to do,

109
00:07:06,790 --> 00:07:08,200
I'll give you this shop.

110
00:07:08,220 --> 00:07:09,620
I'll go rent another shop.

111
00:07:09,650 --> 00:07:11,060
Oh, please don't.

112
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:12,630
I don't want to run a shop.

113
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:13,560
Then...

114
00:07:13,580 --> 00:07:15,050
what do you want to do?

115
00:07:15,110 --> 00:07:16,200
None of your business.

116
00:07:16,220 --> 00:07:17,530
I've been in Beijing for so many years.

117
00:07:17,630 --> 00:07:18,630
It wasn't for nothing.

118
00:07:18,940 --> 00:07:19,630
Besides,

119
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:21,630
I haven't decided if I'm moving back.

120
00:07:22,500 --> 00:07:23,420
Then you...

121
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:27,030
Xingchi, you're back.

122
00:07:27,050 --> 00:07:27,950
Auntie.

123
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:29,990
When did you come back?

124
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:30,950
Yesterday.

125
00:07:33,530 --> 00:07:35,370
If I'd known, I'd have come with you.

126
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:38,200
You came back yourself? Where are the other two?

127
00:07:38,690 --> 00:07:39,750
They're grown-ups who

128
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:41,130
can buy their own tickets.

129
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:42,350
What's wrong?

130
00:07:42,450 --> 00:07:43,460
Did they fight?

131
00:07:45,630 --> 00:07:46,360
I don't know.

132
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:47,750
Don't worry.

133
00:07:49,390 --> 00:07:51,320
There's still time till the holidays.

134
00:07:51,620 --> 00:07:53,140
Why did you suddenly come back?

135
00:07:54,270 --> 00:07:55,440
Aren't you busy with work?

136
00:07:58,270 --> 00:07:59,670
I was a bit tired before.

137
00:07:59,690 --> 00:08:01,360
So I asked Wanghe for leave.

138
00:08:02,420 --> 00:08:03,420
I came back early

139
00:08:03,670 --> 00:08:04,550
to spend time with you.

140
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:06,230
Were you fired?

141
00:08:06,270 --> 00:08:07,250
No!

142
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:08,390
Really?

143
00:08:08,630 --> 00:08:09,430
Really.

144
00:08:09,850 --> 00:08:11,860
I finished everything before I came back.

145
00:08:17,630 --> 00:08:19,320
You don't have a proper degree.

146
00:08:19,340 --> 00:08:21,820
We don't have experience working in big companies.

147
00:08:22,690 --> 00:08:23,900
You got into Bee

148
00:08:23,930 --> 00:08:25,650
thanks to Wanghe's help.

149
00:08:26,540 --> 00:08:27,270
So,

150
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,460
however tough or tiring it is,

151
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:31,120
you have to work hard.

152
00:08:32,049 --> 00:08:33,650
Don't hold Wanghe back.

153
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:37,730
Alright,

154
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:39,280
I'll go make you some good food.

155
00:08:57,140 --> 00:09:01,040
[Old Street Tofu Pudding Shop]

156
00:09:01,190 --> 00:09:08,890
[Signature honey tofu pudding]

157
00:09:06,430 --> 00:09:07,320
Are you free?

158
00:09:07,950 --> 00:09:08,840
I'll treat you to tea.

159
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:13,890
[Business Hours]

160
00:09:11,150 --> 00:09:13,200
Who drinks tea this late at night?

161
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:13,870
Let's drink alcohol.

162
00:09:15,030 --> 00:09:16,230
But you can barely drink...

163
00:09:16,230 --> 00:09:18,090
I'll keep you company while you drink.

164
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:19,030
Deal?

165
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:20,520
Deal.

166
00:09:20,950 --> 00:09:21,590
Let's go.

167
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:33,560
I remember this place

168
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:35,530
used to be an internet café, right?

169
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,350
Yeah.

170
00:09:36,390 --> 00:09:37,960
We used to come here often.

171
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:41,030
The three of us pretended to be Chris Lee

172
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,320
and chatted with you online.

173
00:09:42,670 --> 00:09:44,030
You even ended up in tears.

174
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,390
How dare you bring that up?

175
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,280
It really upset me.

176
00:09:48,760 --> 00:09:50,210
I'd have killed you guys if Wanghe didn't make it up to me.

177
00:09:55,260 --> 00:09:56,560
How did he make it up?

178
00:09:58,390 --> 00:10:00,390
He took me to Chris Lee's concert.

179
00:10:05,770 --> 00:10:06,920
I bought tickets too.

180
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:11,350
When I arrived that day,

181
00:10:12,790 --> 00:10:14,080
they said you two had just left.

182
00:10:18,880 --> 00:10:21,140
If Chris Lee has another concert,

183
00:10:21,470 --> 00:10:22,470
let's go together.

184
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:26,710
Sure.

185
00:10:27,170 --> 00:10:27,880
Just the two of us.

186
00:10:28,860 --> 00:10:29,620
No one else.

187
00:10:33,270 --> 00:10:33,980
Fenghua.

188
00:10:35,350 --> 00:10:37,230
If you ever get sick of Beijing, are exhausted,

189
00:10:38,270 --> 00:10:39,630
and want to move back home,

190
00:10:41,180 --> 00:10:42,180
I'll join you.

191
00:10:44,310 --> 00:10:45,890
No matter where you go or what you do

192
00:10:46,450 --> 00:10:47,490
in the future,

193
00:10:48,570 --> 00:10:49,790
I'll be with you.

194
00:10:57,270 --> 00:10:58,740
I haven't decided

195
00:10:58,910 --> 00:11:00,030
if I'm moving back.

196
00:11:00,790 --> 00:11:02,270
And I don't need your company.

197
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:05,450
I love being alone now.

198
00:11:05,470 --> 00:11:06,230
Really.

199
00:11:10,100 --> 00:11:11,240
So...

200
00:11:12,810 --> 00:11:14,640
do you plan to stay single forever?

201
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:18,600
In the future...

202
00:11:20,550 --> 00:11:22,240
I'll find someone

203
00:11:22,260 --> 00:11:23,810
who really spoils me.

204
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,720
I'll go wherever I want.

205
00:11:27,670 --> 00:11:28,480
New York,

206
00:11:28,850 --> 00:11:29,560
Paris,

207
00:11:29,970 --> 00:11:30,930
Maldives.

208
00:11:31,730 --> 00:11:33,200
I'll do whatever I want

209
00:11:33,230 --> 00:11:34,630
and eat whatever I want.

210
00:11:35,630 --> 00:11:37,270
He'll send me flowers every day.

211
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,420
I can use his credit card as I please.

212
00:11:39,670 --> 00:11:40,910
And our garage

213
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:42,870
will be overloaded with cars.

214
00:11:44,550 --> 00:11:46,200
I hadn't seen much of the world as a kid.

215
00:11:47,910 --> 00:11:49,270
Even getting free ice cream

216
00:11:49,300 --> 00:11:50,640
made me happy.

217
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:53,390
Now that I'm grown up,

218
00:11:54,670 --> 00:11:56,360
I think it's better to be more practical.

219
00:11:58,880 --> 00:12:00,270
Am I right?

220
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:05,120
You're right.

221
00:12:08,760 --> 00:12:09,390
Come on,

222
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:10,750
let's toast to

223
00:12:11,520 --> 00:12:12,670
our future happiness.

224
00:12:16,500 --> 00:12:17,270
Absolutely.

225
00:12:49,860 --> 00:12:50,500
Still here?

226
00:12:51,670 --> 00:12:52,420
Almost done.

227
00:12:52,790 --> 00:12:54,510
There's still a market analysis that

228
00:12:54,510 --> 00:12:55,670
Finance needs to review.

229
00:12:56,870 --> 00:12:58,480
It's a day before New Year’s Eve.

230
00:12:58,550 --> 00:12:59,960
Not going back to your hometown?

231
00:13:00,550 --> 00:13:02,750
I'll finish it and then drive back

232
00:13:02,750 --> 00:13:03,650
right away.

233
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:05,850
Don't push yourself.

234
00:13:06,510 --> 00:13:07,670
I'll stay with my mom for the Eve.

235
00:13:07,670 --> 00:13:09,870
Let's drive back together on the 2nd or 3rd of the New Year.

236
00:13:10,670 --> 00:13:12,400
Just spend time with your mom.

237
00:13:12,670 --> 00:13:13,270
I need to go back.

238
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:14,790
I need to talk to Fenghua.

239
00:13:15,510 --> 00:13:16,550
Can't you talk over the phone?

240
00:13:17,510 --> 00:13:18,080
No,

241
00:13:18,790 --> 00:13:19,870
I must talk to her in person.

242
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:22,030
Alright then.

243
00:13:22,100 --> 00:13:23,580
Be careful on the road later.

244
00:13:23,630 --> 00:13:24,360
I'll be off then.

245
00:13:24,980 --> 00:13:26,000
Say hello to your mom for me.

246
00:13:26,030 --> 00:13:26,940
Go home soon.

247
00:13:27,010 --> 00:13:27,700
Drive safely.

248
00:14:31,240 --> 00:14:32,180
Aunt Yan.

249
00:14:34,140 --> 00:14:35,780
Wanghe, you're back for the New Year.

250
00:14:36,530 --> 00:14:37,390
How did you come back?

251
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:38,720
By car or plane?

252
00:14:38,740 --> 00:14:39,580
I drove.

253
00:14:40,250 --> 00:14:41,010
Where's Fenghua?

254
00:14:42,880 --> 00:14:44,260
Looking for her as soon as you're back?

255
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:45,700
That girl

256
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:47,440
came back without saying a word

257
00:14:47,470 --> 00:14:48,460
and didn't wait for me.

258
00:14:48,500 --> 00:14:49,500
So disloyal.

259
00:14:49,530 --> 00:14:51,040
I know. That child...

260
00:14:51,070 --> 00:14:53,390
It'd have been nice to come back together!

261
00:14:53,390 --> 00:14:55,150
I'll call her. She's sleeping.

262
00:14:58,880 --> 00:14:59,610
Fenghua.

263
00:14:59,630 --> 00:15:00,590
Fenghua.

264
00:15:00,910 --> 00:15:01,600
Fenghua?

265
00:15:01,630 --> 00:15:03,000
Wanghe is back.

266
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:06,800
Still sleeping in.

267
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:07,750
When she wakes up,

268
00:15:07,770 --> 00:15:09,290
I'll tell her to find you.

269
00:15:09,640 --> 00:15:11,250
Still sleeping at this hour?

270
00:15:11,520 --> 00:15:14,060
She went out drinking with Xingchi yesterday.

271
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:15,370
She came back at midnight.

272
00:15:16,280 --> 00:15:17,200
Go rest at home.

273
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:18,810
You must be tired from driving.

274
00:15:18,830 --> 00:15:20,070
Come here to eat when you're hungry.

275
00:15:21,160 --> 00:15:23,200
I'll tell her to find you when she wakes up.

276
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:24,160
Alright.

277
00:15:35,470 --> 00:15:36,440
I applied

278
00:15:37,170 --> 00:15:38,370
for your leave with Meng.

279
00:15:39,170 --> 00:15:40,710
Your year-end bonus was cut by 70%.

280
00:15:45,580 --> 00:15:46,490
It doesn't matter.

281
00:15:48,210 --> 00:15:49,790
I expected nothing anyway.

282
00:16:07,410 --> 00:16:08,460
Save some for me.

283
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:10,910
You don't deserve it.

284
00:16:14,030 --> 00:16:15,010
Because of you,

285
00:16:15,990 --> 00:16:17,670
the delivery riders at Station 203

286
00:16:18,210 --> 00:16:19,660
aren't getting year-end bonuses.

287
