852
00:41:28,400 --> 00:41:30,230
But you refused without a second thought.

853
00:41:30,230 --> 00:41:31,360
I don't want to buy a house

854
00:41:32,280 --> 00:41:34,000
because I don't want to spend my family's money.

855
00:41:34,710 --> 00:41:36,190
I want to rely on my own efforts.

856
00:41:36,190 --> 00:41:37,810
But I can't wait any longer.

857
00:41:38,960 --> 00:41:40,790
I'm almost 30 years old.

858
00:41:41,710 --> 00:41:43,550
After all these years in Beijing,

859
00:41:43,760 --> 00:41:45,230
among my college roommates,

860
00:41:45,230 --> 00:41:46,980
even the least successful one lives in Swan Bay

861
00:41:47,030 --> 00:41:48,190
and drives an X5.

862
00:41:49,670 --> 00:41:50,440
But me?

863
00:41:50,840 --> 00:41:53,030
I have to be alert every time I take a cab.

864
00:41:53,360 --> 00:41:55,110
When there's traffic and the driver takes a detour,

865
00:41:55,110 --> 00:41:56,280
I start to panic.

866
00:41:58,880 --> 00:42:00,670
I'm a graduate from a top university.

867
00:42:01,160 --> 00:42:02,800
I've won first-class scholarships.

868
00:42:02,840 --> 00:42:04,820
Is this any way for me to live?

869
00:42:10,040 --> 00:42:10,600
Being poor

870
00:42:11,930 --> 00:42:13,010
is still the original sin, huh?

871
00:42:13,030 --> 00:42:14,220
Haikuo.

872
00:42:15,410 --> 00:42:17,430
I know you've been trying hard,

873
00:42:17,790 --> 00:42:19,270
but I'm sorry.

874
00:42:20,220 --> 00:42:21,900
I no longer have the time

875
00:42:22,320 --> 00:42:24,920
or patience to chase after your empty promises.

876
00:42:26,800 --> 00:42:28,070
Do you get what I'm saying?

877
00:42:28,510 --> 00:42:29,260
Yes.

878
00:42:46,940 --> 00:42:48,320
You again?

879
00:42:51,880 --> 00:42:52,630
Officer Xia.

880
00:42:52,790 --> 00:42:54,540
Didn't you get a proper job?

881
00:42:55,000 --> 00:42:56,440
Why are you causing trouble again?

882
00:42:56,880 --> 00:42:58,000
He deserved a beating.

883
00:42:59,480 --> 00:43:00,800
If you were me, you'd have hit him too.

884
00:43:01,560 --> 00:43:03,080
Don't tell me all that.

885
00:43:03,100 --> 00:43:04,310
Tell that to your superior.

886
00:43:07,920 --> 00:43:08,710
My superior?
